short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Step into One Piece with Yamato! This extension brings the fierce warrior’s spirit to your new tab with an epic live wallpaper.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Step into the world of One Piece with Yamato! This Chrome extension brings the spirit of Yamato, the fierce warrior, to your new tab in an epic live wallpaper.

The Yamato One Piece live wallpaper extension showcases this beloved character against a stunning backdrop inspired by the anime’s iconic visuals. Designed for fans, it combines a bold aesthetic with a user-friendly browsing experience.

Effortlessly search the web with the Google search bar, access favorite sites using customizable shortcuts, and stay updated with a clock-date display.

Key Features:

Live Wallpaper featuring Yamato from One Piece
Google Search Bar for easy navigation
Customizable site shortcuts for quick access
Clock-Date display to stay organized

Set sail with Yamato every time you open a new tab! Discover more anime-themed wallpapers at Gameograf.com to personalize your browsing.
